<a href="/questions/584402-i-wasn-t-very-specific-i-am-looking-for">I wasn&#39;t very specific. I am looking for chapter books. I am currently working with &quot;For Reading Out Loud&quot; by Margaret Mary Kimmel and Elizabeth Segel. It was published in 1983. It&#39;s a great book, but I know a lot has been written in the past 30 years. ?</a>
