<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Sarah Mackenzie&apos;s The Read Aloud Family is heavily inspired by this book and she made a point to cater her recommendations mostly to the best books of<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Sarah Mackenzie's The Read Aloud Family is heavily inspired by this book and she made a point to cater her recommendations mostly to the best books of recent decades. I know your request is old but hopefully it helps someone else.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
